    <string name="terms_title">PRIVACY &amp; TERMS</string>
    <string name="terms_section_1_title">1. WHO WE ARE</string>
    <string name="terms_section_1_body">Swanie\'s Portfolio is developed and published by the Swanie\'s Portfolio team. For support questions, use the contact method listed in this app\'s Google Play listing.</string>
    <string name="terms_section_2_title">2. HOW YOUR DATA IS STORED</string>
    <string name="terms_section_2_body">This app is designed to store your portfolio content primarily on your device, including vault/login data, holdings, preferences, and app configuration needed for normal use.</string>
    <string name="terms_section_3_title">3. OPTIONAL NETWORK FEATURES</string>
    <string name="terms_section_3_body">This version keeps your vault on your device and does not automatically sync it to Google Drive (that is planned for a future release). Optional network features include Google Play billing/subscriptions when you purchase, optional feedback if you submit it, and market-data providers when prices load. Encrypted backup is a file you export and store yourself.</string>
    <string name="terms_section_4_title">4. DATA LIMITS AND ACCESS</string>
    <string name="terms_section_4_body">We do not sell your personal data. Features are designed for minimal collection and user-controlled access. Due to local encryption design, account/password recovery may be limited if credentials are lost.</string>
    <string name="terms_section_5_title">5. NO FINANCIAL ADVICE</string>
    <string name="terms_section_5_body">Swanie\'s Portfolio is a tracking tool. Market and pricing data may come from third-party providers. We are not responsible for market fluctuations or external data accuracy.</string>
    <string name="terms_section_6_title">6. CHILDREN, LANGUAGE, AND POLICY CHANGES</string>
    <string name="terms_section_6_body">This app is not directed to children under 13. English is the master legal language for this app. We may update this policy over time; the latest version is reflected by the date shown below and on our website privacy page.</string>
    <string name="terms_section_7_title">7. LIMITATION OF LIABILITY; INDEMNITY; USE AT YOUR OWN RISK</string>
    <string name="terms_section_7_body">By downloading, installing, or using Swanie\'s Portfolio, you agree on behalf of yourself and anyone you represent that, to the fullest extent permitted by applicable law, you will not hold Swanie\'s Portfolio, its developers, contractors, licensors, or agents liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, exemplary, or punitive damages, or for any loss of profits, data, goodwill, business interruption, or investment losses, including damages or losses arising from: your use or inability to use the app; reliance on prices, charts, analytics, or other content in the app; errors, bugs, or interruptions; loss or corruption of local data, credentials, or backups; or third-party services or data sources. The app is provided on an \"AS IS\" and \"AS AVAILABLE\" basis without warranties of any kind, whether express or implied, including implied warranties of merchantability, fitness for a particular purpose, title, or non-infringement, except where such disclaimers are prohibited by law. You agree to indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Swanie\'s Portfolio and its developers, contractors, licensors, and agents from any claims, liabilities, damages, losses, costs, or expenses (including reasonable attorneys\' fees) arising from your use of the app, your violation of these terms, or your violation of any third party\'s rights. Some jurisdictions do not allow certain limitations or exclusions; in those cases, our liability is limited to the maximum extent permitted by law. If any remedy is required and a cap is permitted, our aggregate liability for any claim relating to the app shall not exceed the greater of (a) the amounts you paid us for the app or in-app purchases through Google Play in the twelve (12) months before the claim, or (b) zero if you did not make any such payments. This section survives termination of your use of the app. If you do not agree, do not use the app.</string>
